	<body>
		<p begin="00:00:00.50" end="00:00:03.70">Maria: Ciao, Paolo! Come va?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:00.50" end="00:00:03.70">Maria: Ciao, Paolo! Come va?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:03.70" end="00:00:05.63">Paolo: Bene, tu?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:05.63" end="00:00:07.47">Maria: Bene, grazie.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:07.47" end="00:00:09.32">Dove vai adesso?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:09.32" end="00:00:11.24">Paolo: Vado al lavoro.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:11.24" end="00:00:14.52">Maria: Sì? Dove lavori?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:14.52" end="00:00:17.63">Paolo: Lavoro in un ristorante.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:17.63" end="00:00:20.14">Maria: Come si chiama?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:20.14" end="00:00:23.36">Paolo: Si chiama Trattoria Margherita.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:23.36" end="00:00:26.03">È in via San Daniele.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:26.03" end="00:00:29.41">Maria: Lavori anche il fine settimana?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:29.41" end="00:00:33.73">Paolo: A volte, ma sabato prossimo vado al mare.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:33.73" end="00:00:35.33">Maria: Che bello!</p>
		<p begin="00:00:35.33" end="00:00:36.77">Dove vai?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:36.77" end="00:00:39.44">Paolo: Vado a Ostia.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:39.44" end="00:00:42.57">Maria: Mia zia abita ad Ostia.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:42.57" end="00:00:44.68">È un bel paese.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:44.68" end="00:00:47.26">Paolo: Tu vai via sabato?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:47.26" end="00:00:53.11">Maria: No, vado in centro a comprare un regalo per un&apos;amica.</p>
	</body>
